es of a team winning by 10 wickets. The highest target reached without losing a wicket is 184 by [[Kolkata Knight Riders]] against [[Gujarat Lions]] in April 2017.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/records/305293.html|title=Largest margin of victory (by wickets)|website=Cricinfo|access-date=21 February 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Highest match aggregate===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Score\n! Teams\n! Venue\n! Date\n|-\n| 1\n| 497/7 (40 overs)\n| [[Otago cricket team|Otago]] (249/3) v [[Central Districts cricket team|Central Districts]] (248/4)\n| [[Pukekura Park|New Plymouth, Taranaki]]\n| 21 December 2016\n|-\n| 2\n| 493/7 (40 overs)\n| [[Trinbago Knight Riders]] (267/2) v  [[Jamaica Tallawahs]]  (226/5)\n| [[Sabina Park|Kingston, Jamaica]]\n| 13 September 2019\n|-\n| 3\n| 489/10 (40 overs)\n| {{cr|WIN}} (245/6) v {{cr|IND}} (244/4) \n| [[Central Broward Regional Park|Lauderhill, Florida]]\n| 27 August 2016\n|-\n| 4\n| 488/11 (38.5 overs)\n| {{cr|NZ}} (243/6) (H) v {{cr|AUS}} (245/5)\n| [[Eden Park|Auckland]]\n| 16 February 2018\n|-\n| 5\n| 483/10 (38.5 overs)\n| [[Jamaica Tallawahs]] (241/4) v [[St Kitts & Nevis Patriots|SKN Patriots]] (242/6)\n| [[Warner Park Sporting Complex|Basseterre]]\n| 10 September 2019\n|-\n|colspan=\"5\"| <small>Source: [http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/records/305303.html ESPNcricinfo] (Updated 16 September 2019) </small>\n|}\n\n==Individual records==\n===Individual records (batting)===\n====Highest individual score====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n!Rank\n!Runs\n!Player\n!Team\n!Opponent\n!Venue\n!Date\n|-\n|1||175*|| [[Chris Gayle]] || [[Royal Challengers Bangalore]] || [[Pune Warriors India]] || [[M.Chinnaswamy Stadium|Bangalore]] || 23 April 2013\n|-\n|2||172||[[Aaron Finch]]|| {{cr|AUS}} || {{cr|ZIM}} ||[[Harare Sports Club]]||3 July 2018\n|-\n|3||162*||[[Hamilton Masakadza]]||[[Mountaineers cricket team|Mountaineers]]||[[Eagles cricket team|Eagles]]||[[Bulawayo]]||11 Februa