ractive Xbox Girlfriend\">{{cite web |url=https://www.siliconera.com/2012/02/18/the-interactive-xbox-girlfriend-from-microsoft-the-world-never-saw/ |title=The Interactive Xbox Girlfriend From Microsoft The World Never Saw |author=Spencer |date=February 18, 2012 |website=[[Siliconera]] |access-date=October 30, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107023826/http://www.siliconera.com/2012/02/18/the-interactive-xbox-girlfriend-from-microsoft-the-world-never-saw/ |archive-date=November 7, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Siliconera: Miyamoto\">{{cite web |url=https://www.siliconera.com/2012/02/18/angel-studios-now-rockstar-san-diego-worked-on-an-unreleased-game-with-miyamoto/ |title=Angel Studios, Now Rockstar San Diego, Worked On A Game With Miyamoto |author=Spencer |date=February 18, 2012 |website=[[Siliconera]] |access-date=October 30, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107021640/http://www.siliconera.com/2012/02/18/angel-studios-now-rockstar-san-diego-worked-on-an-unreleased-game-with-miyamoto/ |archive-date=November 7, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Free Library: Dream Team\">{{cite web |url=https://www.thefreelibrary.com/ANGEL+STUDIOS+JOINS+NINTENDO+ULTRA+64+DREAM+TEAM%3B+World+renowned...-a016516585 |title=ANGEL STUDIOS JOINS NINTENDO ULTRA 64 DREAM TEAM; World renowned computer graphics studio makes transition from \"The Lawnmower Man\" and MTV award-winning music videos to develop game for Nintendo's 64-bit home video game system. |first1=Alison |last1=Holt Brummelkamp |first2=Scott |last2=Smith |date=February 15, 1995 |website=[[The Free Library]] |access-date=November 26, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171024153005/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/ANGEL+STUDIOS+JOINS+NINTENDO+ULTRA+64+DREAM+TEAM%3b+World+renowned...-a016516585 |archive-date=October 24, 2017 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Washington Post: Lawnmower Man\">{{cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive